<D>__{your honor, ladies and gentlemen of the }
<P>__{(he remembers there's no jury)}
<D>__{audience. i don't think it's fair to call my clients frauds. okay, the blackout was a big problem for everybody. i was stuck in an elevator for about three hours and i had to go to the bathroom the whole time, but i don't blame them because once i turned into a dog and they helped me. thank you.}
