<C>__{judge}
<D>__{that was unquestionably the worst presentation of a case i've ever heard in a court of law! i ought to cite you for contempt and have you disbarred. as for your clients, peter venkman, raymond stantz and egon spengler, on the charges of conspiracy, fraud and the willful destruction of public property, i find you guilty on all counts. i order you to pay fines in the amount of $25,000 each and i sentence you to eighteen months in the city correctional facility at ryker's island.}
